```plantuml
@startuml gregoryjohnsonjg6_angular-dotnet-core-docker

actor User

participant "Angular Frontend" as FE
participant "NGINX Load Balancer" as LB
participant "ASP.NET Core Web API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> FE: Access application
FE -> LB: Send HTTP Request
LB -> API: Forward request

alt User Authentication
    API -> API: Validate JWT Token
else CRUD Operation
    API -> DB: Execute SQL Command
    DB --> API: Return Data
end

API -> LB: Return HTTP Response
LB -> FE: Forward response
FE -> User: Display result

@enduml
```